Initiate = to start formally
We will initiate the project next week.


Drive = to lead or push forward
She is driving this initiative.


Enhance = improve quality
We need to enhance customer experience.


Align with = agree/support
This aligns with our company goals.


Address = deal with a problem
We need to address this issue quickly.


Consolidate = combine things
Let’s consolidate all reports into one.


Delegate = assign work to others
The manager will delegate tasks.


Assess = evaluate
We need to assess the situation.


Onboard = bring someone into team/company
We will onboard new employees next week.


Deliver value = give useful results
Our goal is to deliver value to clients.




